# Preservation repo: keep every file byte-for-byte as it is on disk.
# Disable all line-ending normalization (the 1993 .txt notes use CRLF, and the
# binaries / disk image must never be touched).
* -text

# Be explicit about the binary originals so GitHub treats them as binary.
*.mgt   binary
*.BIN   binary
ARCHIV     binary
UNPAK      binary
IMPLODER   binary
COMPRES    binary
DEC        binary
PASS       binary
PASS1      binary
MDOS23     binary
CrunchCode binary
SCREENCOM1 binary
Lib?v21    binary
